<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">Hello&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Retail_Live_Email__c.OwnerFirstName},</font></div><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" size="3"><br></font></font><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">You have successfully created a Retail LIVE email but there was an issue mapping it to either a BRAND or a VILLAGE using hashtag #, or your VR user record does not have an associated Department.<o:p></o:p></span></p><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Brand:</b>&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Retail_Live_Email__c.Brand_Reference__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Village:</b>&nbsp;{!Retail_Live_Email__c.Village__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Department:</b>&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Retail_Live_Email__c.Department__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Please amend this Retail LIVE email by clicking the link below&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><a href="https://valueretail.my.salesforce.com/{!Retail_Live_Email__c.Id}">https://valueretail.my.salesforce.com/{!Retail_Live_Email__c.Id}</a></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" color="#3366ff"><b>How Tagging works</b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">To&nbsp;automatically&nbsp;associate Retail LIVE emails to Villages &amp; Brands you must include 2 tag references in the&nbsp;<i>body</i>&nbsp;of your Retail LIVE email.<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><font size="3"><br></font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">In this order<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"># followed by your 2-digit Village code: &nbsp;BV, LR, LZ, LV, FV, MV, WV, IV, KV<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"># followed by the Brand name,&nbsp;<u>no spaces</u><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><font size="3"><br></font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Example, to&nbsp;associate a Retail LIVE email with Bicester&nbsp;&amp; Ted Baker you must enter the following in the body of the email.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">#BV<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">#TedBaker<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;"><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;">Tip!</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Add &nbsp;"+++" to remove all signature information from the Retail LIVE email so this information does not get posted to the dashboard keeping everything neat and tidy.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">#BV<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">#TedBaker<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">+++<o:p></o:p></span></p></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Thank you,</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Retail LIVE Team</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
